message: Fixed spelling mistakes,added and fixed Turkish translations,fixed misinformation about a city's name and what is was called. Linked a couple of articles relating to the topic that should be here.
Many of these troops participated in combat the few of was very misleading. This was an important change.
Added a note about the name to stop any confusion and linked another article for more info.
Fixed a slightly incorrect translation and fixed a couple of accent marks that don't exist in Turkish with the correct letter.
A fix to two incorrect things.
